Saurin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/Yurofan Tattalin Arziki da Birtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yanayin da ya yi daidai da na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakan sun bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, COVID-19 ya sami ci gaba mai sauri a duk ƙasashe.
A cewar kwarewar Italiya, kasashen, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa na bukatar kara kasancewa a shirye don magance yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na 2019, an sanar da jerin abubuwan da suka faru na girgizar kasa da ba a san dalilinsa ba a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana dalilin cutar da ake kira Coronavirus, wanda yanzu ake kira Coronavirus, cuta ta 2 na cutar sankarar cuta ta huhu, 2-SARS-CoV.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar ta kamuwa da cuta ta 2-SARS-CoV ta zama sananne da cutar coronavirus COVID-19.
Shaidar ta nuna cewa har zuwa yau, kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna da wani abu mai sauƙi, wato kamuwa da cutar huhu ba tare da kamuwa da cutar huhu ba ko kuma suna da cutar huhu, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
Kashi 14% na waɗanda suka kamu da COVID-19 suna bukatar a kwantar da su a asibiti, kuma kashi 6% na sauran marasa lafiya suna bukatar a yi musu asibiti sosai.
Yawan mutuwar mutane da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 a cikin gidajen da ke barci ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu tantance yanayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Birtaniya kuma mu kwatanta shi da yanayin lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Muna kuma kwatanta yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da bunkasa a wurare dabam-dabam kuma ya sami karuwar cutar a sauran ƙasashe a duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana cutar COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
A ranar 5 ga watan Maris, a cewar Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokansa sun ba da rahoton farkon kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a Turai, a cewar WHO.
A cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, an samu mutum uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hobei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU 30/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya, wanda ya haifar da adadin kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da suka shafi mutuwar 1,727 a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 a Italiya kadai.
Samun yawan masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana samun adadin adadin adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe a duniya daga kafofin na hukuma kamar Ma'aikatun Kiwon Lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na yanki da WHO, kuma ana sabunta su a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan ne don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU da Birtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin mai hana ci gaban COVID-19 a cikin al'amuran da suka shafi cutar, mun yi nazarin rage yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 don yin la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a kowace kasa da aka samu a karfe 8:00 na safe na ranar 15 ga watan Maris, idan aka kwatanta da wadanda aka samu a Italiya a cikin watan 31 ga watan Janairu zuwa 15 ga watan Maris.
Hanyar COVID-19 a cikin EU da Birtaniya
Matsakaicin yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 a cikin EU da Birtaniya sun kasance daidai da na lardin Hubei a China (Figure 1.
A cikin EU da Birtaniya gaba ɗaya, yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma ya sami ci gaba mai yawa a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Wannan ya fi yawaita ne saboda yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma sauran kasashen EU da Birtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da ke dauke da sinadarai.
Shafin 2 ya nuna yawan adadin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Wannan ya nuna cewa a karfe 8:00 na safe na ranar 15 ga watan Maris, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a wasu kasashe 15 na EU da Birtaniya ya yi daidai da adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da Birtaniya suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri.
Bayanan da aka samu na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa wannan kamuwa da cutar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya faru ne duk da cewa ƙasashe ba sa cikin yanayi iri ɗaya a cikin yanayin amsawar lafiyar jama'a ta ƙasa, kuma akwai bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar yanayin da kuma hanyoyin yin gwaji don tabbatar da kamuwa da COVID-19.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar ta COVID-19 a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa ta ICU.
Bayanai na kwancewar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai yanzu suna cikin kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in (ba a bayyana bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara wannan bayanan a cikin tsari don kammala bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan adadin shari'o'in da aka bayar da rahoton da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a watan Nuwamba na 2010 ya nuna bambanci mai yawa a cikin yawan wuraren da ake samun wuraren kulawa da ICU da kuma cibiyoyin kula da lafiya a Turai, inda a Jamus wannan adadi ya kai 29.2 da kuma a Portugal 4.2 a kowace mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nuna cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙasa da ƙasa ko kuma mafi yawan albarkatu idan aka kwatanta da Italiya (wurin yin asibiti na ICU da na ICU na 12.5 ga kowane mutane 100,000 a watan Nuwamba na 2020).
Yanayin da aka tsara game da yadda ake kula da lafiyar jiki, tare da ƙididdigar kowace ƙasa a cikin EU da UK game da yaduwar yanayin COVID-19 da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin sama da 90% na karuwar ƙarfin kwanciyar hankali, ya bayyana a cikin sabuntawar ECDC ta shida na COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment.
Tun da yake akwai cututtuka a cikin EU da Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa suna kula da yawan jama'a a wani yanki, ya fi kyau a karɓi bayanai game da cututtuka da wuraren kulawa da gaggawa daga cikin ƙididdigar ƙididdigar yanki na matakin 2 (NUTS).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa COVID-19 yana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU da Birtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa na bukatar su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da watsa cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya da kuma a wasu lokuta, kamar yadda ake yi a yanzu a yankunan da aka kamu da su na Italiya.
A cikin sabon kimantaccen hadarin ECDC, an kuma bukaci a yi aiki da hanzari a cikin gaggawa, a yi amfani da shi don rage yaduwar cutar ta coronavirus 2-SARS-COV, tare da sauya tsarin daga dakatarwar zuwa jinkiri, saboda a yayin da ake ganin an yi saurin karuwa a yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar, ba za a samu cikakken lokaci ba ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimtar, daidaitawa da daidaitawa da kuma amsawa idan ya yiwu.
Ana yin kimantawa na gaggawa da kuma matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don daidaita tasirin cutar.
Yanzu akwai wani karamin dama ga kasashen da za su iya yin kokarin rage yaduwar cutar ta coronavirus 2-SARS-CoV da kuma kara rage matsin lamba a kan bangaren kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan ya gaza, tsarin kula da lafiyar sauran kasashen EU zai shawo kan yawan marasa lafiya da ke cikin ICU a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
