Kamar yadda yake da irin wannan cutar, wato, SARS-CoV, wanda ya yi sanadiyar kamuwa da dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, sabon SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar cutar kumburi kuma ta hanyar irin wannan tsari, ya haifar da bayyanar irin wannan alamar.
Ana samun cututtuka masu tsanani da kuma mutuwar COVID-19 a ƙasa da SARS, amma ana samun karuwar kamuwa da cutar kuma yana shafar tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
Wannan labarin ya ba da amsa ga yawan adadin wallafe-wallafen da ke tattare da wannan sabon cuta, yana ba da cikakken bayani game da yadda ake saurin ci gaba da bincike.
Muna tattauna muhimman abubuwan da ke tattare da ilimin halittu, ilimin halayyar mutum, ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewa, magani, tsinkaya da rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake har yanzu akwai wasu tambayoyi da za a iya amsawa, muna fatan wannan kimantawa za ta taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma hana wannan cuta mai tsanani.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da tunawa ga jama'ar kasar Sin saboda sun kasance a gida a duk lokacin hutunsu na makonni bayan barkewar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana kama da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wadda ta haifar da cutar sankarar hanta ta hanyar numfashi (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka, a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sake masa suna coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 kuma ta sake masa suna COVID-19.
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a duk faɗin kasar da kuma wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta samu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 guda 80,000, wanda ya kai 40,000 da suka warke kuma fiye da 3,000 suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "abokin gaba na 1" ne kuma ya fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
A cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an wallafa fiye da 200 na labarai game da COVID-19 da suka shafi ganewar asali, ganewar asali, ganewar asali, ganewar asali da kuma maganin cutar, bayan an fara gano cutar a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma sun gano tsarin kwayoyin halitta na cutar a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan kimantawa na ƙoƙarin sauƙaƙe yanayin bincike a cikin wannan sabon yanayin da sauri a cikin yanayin ci gaba.
A duk lokacin da COVID-19 ya fara, muna ƙoƙarin kwatanta shi da SARS da sauran cututtukan coronavirus da kuma ciwon huhu na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, 2012 generalization).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka sani game da rigakafin cutar da kuma yadda za a yi hasashen ta, da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu gaggawa da ba a amsa su ba.
Ana amfani da kwayar cutar coronavirus a cikin al'ada a matsayin cutar ta mutum, kuma tana haifar da kusan kashi 15% na zazzabi na kowa 4.
Duk da haka, a cikin wannan karni, mun fuskanci kamuwa da cutar coronavirus sau biyu, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da kuma Saudiyya a 2012, kuma da wuri-wuri ya bazu a ƙasashe da yawa a duniya, inda ya sami mummunan kamuwa da cutar da mutuwar.
Wannan yana nufin cewa COVID-19 na yanzu shine kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
An kuma nuna a cikin Figure 1.1, an fara sanar da cutar ta numfashi da ba a bayyana asalinta ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an gano jerin kwayoyin cutar coronavirus.
An yi rahoton mutuwar farko a Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020.
A lokacin, an yi gaggawa a birane, larduna da ƙasashe masu kewaye da shi.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an sanar da kamuwa da cutar a cikin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, kuma an nuna cewa cutar tana da ikon watsawa daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an killace birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da dukkan sassan sufuri na jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga watan Disamba, wani bincike na farko na likita ya bayyana cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da suka kamu da cutar, mutane 21 ne kawai suka samu damar kai tsaye zuwa kasuwar abincin teku, kuma a wannan yanayin, an gano farkon farkon cutar daga tushen dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cewa akwai gaggawa a duniya.
A lokacin da aka ba da rahoton, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk faɗin ƙasar Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya. (Fig. 2.2)
Saboda yanayin yana ci gaba da sauri, za a iya buɗewa zuwa ga ƙarshen lokaci da kuma zurfin haɗakarwa.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an gudanar da bincike mai zurfi a kan marasa lafiya 8,866 wanda ya nuna cewa mutane 4,021 sun kamu da COVID-19 kuma an sake yin sabon hoto a cikin binciken (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya shafi mutane na kowane zamani, amma mafi yawan mutane suna tsakanin shekaru 30 zuwa 65.
Kimanin rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun fi shekaru 50, kaɗan ne daga cikinsu sun fi shekaru 20 da haihuwa, kuma 14 ne kawai suka fi shekaru 10 da haihuwa.
