An kuma gano cewa cutar cytokine ta haifar da sakamako mai yawa na tsarin rigakafi na marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
Cytokine cuta wani nau'i ne na amsawa ga tsarin kamuwa da cuta wanda aka yi ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines, ciki har da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ da MCP-1.
Wadannan cytokines suna tilasta wa ƙwayoyin rigakafi su samar da babban adadin radicals na kyauta wanda shine babban dalilin ARDS da kuma rashin aiki na gabobin jiki.
Ƙarfafa tsarin rigakafi don magance cututtukan cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu ɓoye.
Ana amfani da corticosteroids da toshilizomab, da kuma anti-IL6 monoclonal antigen, don magance cutar cytokine.
Sauran magungunan maganin rigakafi don magance cutar cytokine sun hada da rage tsarin garkuwar jiki ga T-cell, IFN-γ, IL-1 da TNF-cell, da kuma hana JAK; Blinatomab; cytokine-signing activator4; da kuma activating HDAC.
Ana amfani da steroids, a matsayin masu karfafa tsarin rigakafi, don magance SARS don rage yawan cutar.
Bugu da ƙari, steroids ba su da amfani ga cutar SARS da COVID-19 idan aka sha su a cikin abinci mai yawa.
