Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba wa Sin da kokarin da ta yi wajen sarrafawa da kuma hana yaduwar cutar.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta lura da bambancin yaduwar cutar SARS tsakanin 2002-2004. Gwamnatin Sin ta yi zargin cewa ta ɓoye kwayar cutar da ta kawo matsala ga ƙoƙarin hanawa da kawar da cutar da kuma rikicin da ke faruwa a yanzu da gwamnatin tarayya ta "ba da izinin doka don kauce wa cutar a lokacin hutun New York City".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar da gwamnatin tarayya ta yanke na hana zirga-zirga a birnin Wan, wakilin hukumar lafiya ta duniya Gaudin Gallaya ya ce yayin da hakan "ba ya saba wa dokar hana zirga-zirga ta WHO ba" ya kasance babban siginar hana yaduwar cutar a yankin da cutar ta yi tsanani. Ya ce "ba a san tarihin lafiyar jama'a ba". A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, an yi rahoton cewa cutar ta yadu daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen Sin da kuma yawan adadin mutane a wasu ƙasashe. Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta ce barkewar cutar ta zama gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta kasa (PHEIC), karo na shida da ake sanar da gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta kasa a karon farko tun bayan an fara annobar ta a shekara ta 2009.
Babban daraktan hukumar ta kasa ta duniya, Tedros Adhanom, ya ce sanar da dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta kasa ta haifar da "fargabar yaduwar cutar a duniya, musamman a kasashe masu talauci da kuma tsakiya da ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
A cikin martani ga aiwatar da dokar hana zirga-zirga, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa a yi kokarin hana tafiye-tafiye da kasuwanci a duniya" kuma "Ba a ba da umarnin duniya na hana kasuwanci da zirga-zirga".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi wa al'umma ta duniya kira da ta ba da dala miliyan 675 don ba da gudummawar kuɗin don shirya don ƙasashe marasa galihu, tana kira ga kotun tarayya ta goyi bayan ƙasashe da "ba su da tsarin kula da mutanen da ke da cutar, ko da a cikin mawuyacin hali".
Tedros ya kara da cewa "mu samu nasara da kokarinmu na kowa" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya su "ba da karin kudi a yau ko a baya" a ranar 11/2, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana COVID-19 a wani taron manema labarai.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya sanar da cewa babban jami'in asirin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da samar da "dukan sojojin tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a aiki".
An kunna darektan ƙungiyar rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a sakamakon haka, yana ba da damar haɗin gwiwar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ba da izinin WHO don "daidaita kan ƙasashen lafiya yayin da sauran masu ba da shawara za su iya kawo kwarewarsu don haɗa al'umma, tattalin arziki da ci gaban yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 14/2, an ba da gudummawar wani darektan ƙungiyar gudanar da aikin WHO tare da Sin don samar da ƙwararrun masanan duniya da kuma jagororin kiwon lafiya na duniya zuwa ƙasar Sin don taimakawa wajen tantancewa da gudanar da gida "ƙarfin cutar da yaduwar cutar", shirya taron bita da haɗuwa da manyan hukumomin ƙasa da kuma gudanar da balaguron yanki don yanke shawara kan "samar da martani ga ayyukan da ke faruwa ga mutanen da ke zaune a cikin ƙasashe masu nisa da kuma sauran ƙasashe, wanda ya haɗa da tsara birane da ƙauyuka". A ranar 25/2, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da sanarwar cewa "duniya dole ne ta kara shirya don yiwuwar yaduwar cutar coronavirus" ta bayyana cewa yayin da har yanzu ba a kira cutar ba, dole ne kasar ta kasance "a shirye".
A cikin martani ga ci gaban yaduwar cutar a Iran, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta tura tawagar da ta hada kai zuwa Iran don duba halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da cewa tsoron yaduwar cutar coronavirus a duniya zai tashi daga "mai tsanani" zuwa "mai tsanani", wanda aka kiyasta a matsayin mafi girman matakin barazana da damuwa".
Mike Ryan, mai gudanar da shirin gaggawa na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, ya yi gargadin duniya a wata sanarwa cewa "akwai takamaiman gwaji ga dukan gwamnatocin duniya: tashi daga barci.
Wataƙila cutar tana cikin hanya kuma dole ne ku kasance a shirye, "neman hanyoyin da za a amsa daidai zai iya taimaka wa duniya ta guje wa mafi munin ɓangaren cutar".
Sun ce bayanan da aka samu yanzu ba su da wata hujja ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ga sanarwar annobar duniya, suna cewa wannan sanarwar tana nufin "mun yarda cewa kowane mutum a duniya yana da hadarin kamuwa da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cewa annobar korona ta zama annoba.
Darakta janar ya ce WHO "ta yi tunanin cewa cutar ta yi ta yaduwa da ƙarfi da tsanani, kuma matakin da ta yi muni na yaduwar ta yi jinkiri", WHO ta yi magana game da muhimmin kalubalen da ke tattare da wannan ɓangaren annobar, wanda ya haɗa da sanar da dokar ta baci ta gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya ta jama'a da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annoba.
Tunanin jama'a ya hada da korafin zuwa ga babban darektan hukumar lafiya ta duniya, Tedros Adamon, na neman a yi masa murabus, wanda mutane 733,000 suka rattaba hannu a ranar 6 ga watan Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, ƙungiyar kwararrun 'yancin bil adama ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta sake tabbatar da cewa ana girmama hakkokin kowa a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce an ba kowa rai mai lafiya kuma gwamnati ta dauki alhakin hakan.
Kungiyar ta tabbatar da cewa ba za a taba bayar da rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya a matsayin abin karewa ga rabuwa da wani rukuni ba.
Masana sun tabbatar da cewa kowa yana da hakkin kiwon lafiya, ciki har da mutane da ke da nakasa, kungiyoyin 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, 'yan gudun hijira na gida, marasa gida, masu zaman kansu, masu kurkuku, da dubban 'yan gudun hijira da kuma kungiyoyin da ba a san su ba da bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Gwamnatin ƙasa ta yi magana game da tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar al'umma a cikin rikicin COVID-19.
Hukumar Tattalin Arziki da Ci gaban Kasashen Duniya ta kaddamar da dandamali don samar da cikakken bayani game da ayyukan siyasa a ƙasashen duniya, da ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
