Waɗannan ma'aikata suna cikin haɗari idan ma'aikata suka yi amfani da na'urar canja iska ko kuma sun tattara samfurin marasa lafiya ko waɗanda ake zargi da COVID-19.
Na'urar canja iska ta iska don kula da rashin lafiya da na'urar motsa jiki na ɗakin ajiya da na'urar duba iska da wasu na'urori na haƙori da gwaji ko kuma ƙonewa.
